    "body": "The problem comes from placing the artifacts directory inside of the sources one.\r\n\r\nHardhat creates a directory per each `.sol` file that it compiles, with the same name. Then, a successive compilation process will think that those are files, try to read them, and throw that error.\r\n\r\nI think we should improve the error message, and maybe even validate that the artifacts folder isn't inside the sources one, but I don't think we should support this usecase.",
